    "Impact of AI literacy's different dimensions on the effectiveness of using ChatGPT to solve programming problems.",
    "Based on the measurement results of AI awareness, AI usage, AI evaluation, and AI ethics, participants were categorized into high and low AI literacy groups (Yang et al., 2021)."
